data.description: Perfect starter home for your family at an affordable price! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home also includes a 20 x 30 workshop equipped with electricity! It also features a nice back porch that overlooks a fenced in yard, original hardwood floors, exposed wood beams, huge master bedroom with attached office, and a spacious walk in closet! Such a unique home in a convenient location. Walking distance to parks, walking track, churches, restaurants, library, and more. Come check this one out!
